main event: On the night of April 17-19, 1966, multiple observers reported seeing up to 15 unidentified objects over New Castle, Maine.
interesting points: Witnesses noted varied courses of the objects, some reported them as multicolored lights,The sighting lasted approximately two hours,No physical evidence was found,Similar sightings were reported in nearby areas during the same time period.
witness description: Residents of the area, including nearby towns.
